:analysis a schema:Article ;
    schema:name "The End of the AI Buffet: Anthropic's Platform Play" ;
    schema:description "Behind Anthropic's crackdown on third-party tools lies a much bigger shift: the era of subsidised compute is over. The article covers Anthropic's crackdown on third-party tools (OpenClaw ban), the economics of subscription vs API pricing, why models are a weak moat, Anthropic's platform/application layer play, and enterprise vs consumer revenue mix."@en ;
    schema:url <https://substack.com/home/post/p-195014699> ;
